        the harvest will never take place.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "Tremble, you women of ease;\n\tthrow off your complacency.\n\tStrip
        off your pretty clothes,\n\tand put on burlap to show your grief.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "Beat your breasts in sorrow for your bountiful farms\n\tand your
        fruitful grapevines.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "For your land will be overgrown with thorns and briers.\n\tYour joyful
        homes and happy towns will be gone.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
