  - verses:
    - title: Hope for Restoration
      content: "Even the wilderness and desert will be glad in those days.\n\tThe
        wasteland will rejoice and blossom with spring crocuses.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "Yes, there will be an abundance of flowers\n\tand singing and joy!\n\tThe
        deserts will become as green as the mountains of Lebanon,\n\tas lovely as
        Mount Carmel or the plain of Sharon.\n\tThere the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>
        will display his glory,\n\tthe splendor of our God.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "With this news, strengthen those who have tired hands,\n\tand encourage
        those who have weak knees.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "Say to those with fearful hearts,\n\t\u201CBe strong, and do not
        fear,\n\tfor your God is coming to destroy your enemies.\n\tHe is coming
        to save you.\u201D  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "And when he comes, he will open the eyes of the blind\n\tand unplug
        the ears of the deaf.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "The lame will leap like a deer,\n\tand those who cannot speak will
        sing for joy!\n\tSprings will gush forth in the wilderness,\n\tand streams
        will water the wasteland.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "The parched ground will become a pool,\n\tand springs of water will
        satisfy the thirsty land.\n\tMarsh grass and reeds and rushes will flourish\n\twhere
        desert jackals once lived.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "And a great road will go through that once deserted land.\n\tIt will
