          body: 
    - title: 
      content: "A voice said, \u201CShout!\u201D\n\tI asked, \u201CWhat should I
        shout?\u201D\n\t\u201CShout that people are like the grass.\n\tTheir beauty
        fades as quickly\n\tas the flowers in a field.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "The grass withers and the flowers fade\n\tbeneath the breath of the
        <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>\n\t.\n\tAnd so it is with people.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "The grass withers and the flowers fade,\n\tbut the word of our God
        stands forever.\u201D  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "O Zion, messenger of good news,\n\tshout from the mountaintops!\n\tShout
