      comments: []
    - title: "Israel\u2019s Failure to Listen and See"
      content: "\u201CListen, you who are deaf!\n\tLook and see, you blind!  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "Who is as blind as my own people, my servant?\n\tWho is as deaf as
        my messenger?\n\tWho is as blind as my chosen people,\n\tthe servant of the
