    - title: 
      content: "I, yes I, am the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>\n\t,\n\tand there is
        no other Savior.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "First I predicted your rescue,\n\tthen I saved you and proclaimed
