    - title: 
      content: "For the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps> is God,\n\tand he created the
        heavens and earth\n\tand put everything in place.\n\tHe made the world to
        be lived in,\n\tnot to be a place of empty chaos.\n\t\u201CI am the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>\n\t,\u201D
        he says,\n\t\u201Cand there is no other.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "I publicly proclaim bold promises.\n\tI do not whisper obscurities
        in some dark corner.\n\tI would not have told the people of Israel[COMMENT[0]]
        to seek me\n\tif I could not be found.\n\tI, the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>\n\t,
        speak only what is true\n\tand declare only what is right.  "
      comments:
      - number: '45:19 '
        contents:
        - ft: 'Hebrew '
          body: 'of Jacob. '
        - ft: See note on 14:1.
          body: 
    - title: 
      content: "\u201CGather together and come,\n\tyou fugitives from surrounding
        nations.\n\tWhat fools they are who carry around their wooden idols\n\tand
        pray to gods that cannot save!  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "Consult together, argue your case.\n\tGet together and decide what
        to say.\n\tWho made these things known so long ago?\n\tWhat idol ever told
        you they would happen?\n\tWas it not I, the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>\n\t?\n\tFor
        there is no other God but me,\n\ta righteous God and Savior.\n\tThere is
        none but me.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "Let all the world look to me for salvation!\n\tFor I am God; there
        is no other.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "I have sworn by my own name;\n\tI have spoken the truth,\n\tand I
        will never go back on my word:\n\tEvery knee will bend to me,\n\tand every
        tongue will declare allegiance to me.[COMMENT[0]]\u201D  "
      comments:
      - number: '45:23 '
        contents:
        - ft: 'Hebrew '
          body: 'will confess; '
        - ft: 'Greek version reads '
          body: 'will declare allegiance to God. '
        - ft: Compare Rom 14:11.
          body: 
    - title: 
      content: "The people will declare,\n\t\u201CThe <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>
        is the source of all my righteousness and strength.\u201D\n\tAnd all who
        were angry with him\n\twill come to him and be ashamed.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "In the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps> all the generations of Israel
        will be justified,\n\tand in him they will boast."
      comments: []
  - verses:
    - title: "Babylon\u2019s False Gods"
      content: "Bel and Nebo, the gods of Babylon,\n\tbow as they are lowered to
        the ground.\n\tThey are being hauled away on ox carts.\n\tThe poor beasts
        stagger under the weight.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "Both the idols and their owners are bowed down.\n\tThe gods cannot
        protect the people,\n\tand the people cannot protect the gods.\n\tThey go
        off into captivity together.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "\u201CListen to me, descendants of Jacob,\n\tall you who remain in
        Israel.\n\tI have cared for you since you were born.\n\tYes, I carried you
        before you were born.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "I will be your God throughout your lifetime\u2014\n\tuntil your hair
        is white with age.\n\tI made you, and I will care for you.\n\tI will carry
        you along and save you.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "\u201CTo whom will you compare me?\n\tWho is my equal?  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "Some people pour out their silver and gold\n\tand hire a craftsman
        to make a god from it.\n\tThen they bow down and worship it!  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "They carry it around on their shoulders,\n\tand when they set it
        down, it stays there.\n\tIt can\u2019t even move!\n\tAnd when someone prays
        to it, there is no answer.\n\tIt can\u2019t rescue anyone from trouble.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "\u201CDo not forget this! Keep it in mind!\n\tRemember this, you
        guilty ones.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "Remember the things I have done in the past.\n\tFor I alone am God!\n\tI
        am God, and there is none like me.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "Only I can tell you the future\n\tbefore it even happens.\n\tEverything
        I plan will come to pass,\n\tfor I do whatever I wish.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "I will call a swift bird of prey from the east\u2014\n\ta leader
        from a distant land to come and do my bidding.\n\tI have said what I would
        do,\n\tand I will do it.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "\u201CListen to me, you stubborn people\n\twho are so far from doing
        right.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "For I am ready to set things right,\n\tnot in the distant future,
        but right now!\n\tI am ready to save Jerusalem[COMMENT[0]]and show my glory
        to Israel."
      comments:
