    - title: 
      content: "They were not thirsty\n\twhen he led them through the desert.\n\tHe
        divided the rock,\n\tand water gushed out for them to drink.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "\u201CBut there is no peace for the wicked,\u201D\n\tsays the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>\n\t."
