          body: 
    - title: 
      content: "I will say to the prisoners, \u2018Come out in freedom,\u2019\n\tand
        to those in darkness, \u2018Come into the light.\u2019\n\tThey will be my
        sheep, grazing in green pastures\n\tand on hills that were previously bare.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "They will neither hunger nor thirst.\n\tThe searing sun will not
        reach them anymore.\n\tFor the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps> in his mercy will
        lead them;\n\the will lead them beside cool waters.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "And I will make my mountains into level paths for them.\n\tThe highways
        will be raised above the valleys.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "See, my people will return from far away,\n\tfrom lands to the north
        and west,\n\tand from as far south as Egypt.[COMMENT[0]]\u201D  "
      comments:
      - number: '49:12 '
        contents:
        - ft: 'As in Dead Sea Scrolls, which read '
