    - title: 
      content: "Your children will commit themselves to you, O Jerusalem,\n\tjust
        as a young man commits himself to his bride.\n\tThen God will rejoice over
        you\n\tas a bridegroom rejoices over his bride.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "O Jerusalem, I have posted watchmen on your walls;\n\tthey will pray
        day and night, continually.\n\tTake no rest, all you who pray to the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>\n\t.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "Give the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps> no rest until he completes his
        work,\n\tuntil he makes Jerusalem the pride of the earth.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "The <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps> has sworn to Jerusalem by his own
        strength:\n\t\u201CI will never again hand you over to your enemies.\n\tNever
        again will foreign warriors come\n\tand take away your grain and new wine.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "You raised the grain, and you will eat it,\n\tpraising the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>\n\t.\n\tWithin
        the courtyards of the Temple,\n\tyou yourselves will drink the wine you have
        pressed.\u201D  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "Go out through the gates!\n\tPrepare the highway for my people to
        return!\n\tSmooth out the road; pull out the boulders;\n\traise a flag for
        all the nations to see.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "The <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps> has sent this message to every land:\n\t\u201CTell
        the people of Israel,[COMMENT[0]]\u2018Look, your Savior is coming.\n\tSee,
        he brings his reward with him as he comes.\u2019\u201D  "
