        - ft: 'Hebrew '
          body: Javan.
    - title: 
      content: "They will bring the remnant of your people back from every nation.
        They will bring them to my holy mountain in Jerusalem as an offering to the
        <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>\n\t. They will ride on horses, in chariots and
        wagons, and on mules and camels,\u201D says the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>\n\t. "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "\u201CAnd I will appoint some of them to be my priests and Levites.
        I, the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>\n\t, have spoken!  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "\u201CAs surely as my new heavens and earth will remain,\n\tso will
        you always be my people,\n\twith a name that will never disappear,\u201D\n\tsays
        the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>\n\t.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "\u201CAll humanity will come to worship me\n\tfrom week to week\n\tand
        from month to month.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "And as they go out, they will see\n\tthe dead bodies of those who
        have rebelled against me.\n\tFor the worms that devour them will never die,\n\tand
        the fire that burns them will never go out.\n\tAll who pass by\n\twill view
        them with utter horror.\u201D"
      comments: []
